<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.3.5">
<l>āṅkuven narakatta ḻuntumpō tañcē leṉṟaṭi yēṉaiyaṅ kēvantu</l>
<l>tāṅkutāma raiyaṉṉa poṉṉāra ṭiyempirā ṉaiyum parkka ṇiyāyniṉṟa</l>
<l>vēṅkaṭat tariyaip parikīṟi yaiveṇṇe yuṇṭura liṉiṭai yāppuṇṭa</l>
<l>tīṅkarumpi ṉaitēṉai naṉpā liṉaiyaṉṟi yeṉmaṉañ cintaicey yātē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without my lord with lotus-like feet adorned in gold who,</l>
<l rend="indent">when I then sink into fiery hell,</l>
<l>Will then protect me, his servant, coming there saying, “Don’t fear,”</l>
<l>The lion of Vēṅkaṭa who endures as an ornament for the gods,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who split the horse,</l>
<l>The sweet sugarcane who, having eaten butter, was tied, [my] honey,</l>
<l rend="indent">fine milk, my mind does not produce thoughts.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
